{"type":"message","id":"9eed4634","parentId":"d8490b0e","timestamp":"2026-03-23T20:45:48.848Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Two subagents are running in parallel. Let me wait for their results. In the meantime, let me check if there's anything else I can do.Actually, looking at the time (04:43 AM), the news-market skill might fail because:\n1. Chinese market data sources might not have data at this hour (before market open)\n2. It might work fine since it pulls from web sourcesLet me also think about what to do about the control tower files. Even if the news is generated, the control tower won't be updated until the `run_investment_research_org_publish_bundle.py` runs at 09:32.\n\nActually, wait - let me re-read the health check more carefully. The ALERT shows `morning_news_ok: False`. But `morning_news_ok` comes from the control tower JSON. The control tower JSON is generated by the `run_investment_research_org_publish_bundle.py` script.\n \nSo the core issue is that the publish bundle script needs to run first to create the control tower JSON, and only then can the health check validate against it. The news-market script generates the news report separately, but that's just one component - the publish bundle is what ties everything together and produces the control tower that the health check actually reads.\n\nThe NEWS_MARKET_0850 cron job appears to run at 08:50 on weekdays, though I'm not entirely sure if that's when the control tower gets updated or if it's a separate process. Since the cron hasn't executed yet today, I should probably just run the news generation now to get it started, but the full control tower and health check validation will have to wait until the cron jobs actually run.","thinkingSignature":"c6c163c3a0ca34913e8207533c5864c65cd36d0e585cf1f2dff27b080a43b3b8"},{"type":"text","text":"已派出两个并行子任务：\n1. **morning-news-generator** — 立即生成今日晨报（早于 cron 08:50）\n2. **strategy-backtest-check** — 检查策略审计 + 回测队列状态\n\n等待子任务结果返回。期间让我查一下最近的策略审计和回测队列状态：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7r6xdae98ban_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/ | grep -E \"strategy_audit.*2026032[123].*\\.json\" 2>/dev/null; ls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/ | grep -E \"strategy_audit.*2026032[123]\" | sort | tail -3"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7r6xdae98ban_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/ | grep -E \"backtest_queue.*2026032[123]\" | sort | tail -3"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":16085,"output":562,"cacheRead":37996,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54643,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774298737266}}
