{"type":"message","id":"27c22680","parentId":"69bffa9f","timestamp":"2026-03-24T07:43:58.734Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Self-improvement already ran today at 15:14. Morning news is OK (08:50 success). Let me now run the live dashboard for the afternoon. It's 15:43, after trading hours. Let me check the live dashboard generation and push.\n\nActually, it's 15:43 which is after 15:00 market close. Let me spawn the live dashboard and push.","thinkingSignature":"1bfda5b3ed49e269810b96686bec1bc8d391c0a11e516ca375db4dcbaebebf19"},{"type":"text","text":"晨报 OK，self-improvement 已完成（15:14）。现在执行收盘后的实盘面板生成与推送：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g1v74xnjpeai_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"生成收盘后实盘总览面板并推送飞书。\n\n执行以下命令（按顺序）：\n```bash\ncd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\n\n# 1. 同步同花顺数据\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py 2>&1\n\n# 2. 同步同花顺导出\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_exports.py 2>&1\n\n# 3. 生成实盘面板\npython3 scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py 2>&1\n```\n\n然后将面板关键信息（面板路径、precheck状态、年化/回撤/夏普、买卖记录数、A股温度摘要）推送到飞书 DM 给张玲。\n\n如果需要权限（needs_permission=true），告知需要给终端 Full Disk Access。\n\n如果导出为空，告知\"同花顺暂无可用导出数据/账户为空\"。\n\n完成后汇报：\n1. 各命令输出摘要\n2. 生成的面板文件路径\n3. 飞书推送状态\n4. 如有异常，说明原因\n","label":"live-dashboard-pm","runtime":"subagent","runTimeoutSeconds":180,"mode":"run"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":30248,"output":404,"cacheRead":38317,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68969,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774338224773}}
