{"type":"message","id":"90e32d3a","parentId":"b5c2849d","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:20:18.987Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Read HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 24th, 2026 — 9:20 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-24 13:20 UTC"}],"timestamp":1774358418985}}
{"type":"message","id":"48086f83","parentId":"90e32d3a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:20:36.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Heartbeat at 21:20 (9:20 PM) Shanghai time. Let me check what needs attention.\n\nRules from HEARTBEAT.md:\n- Quiet hours 23:00-08:00: keep quiet for non-urgent\n- Only three types of proactive reports:\n  1. New files/reports are ready\n  2. Scripts have produced results\n  3. Need user input/authorization\n\nCurrent time: 21:20 (9:20 PM) - this is within quiet hours (23:00-08:00)? No, 21:20 is 9:20 PM, which is before 23:00. So quiet hours haven't started yet (quiet hours are 23:00 to 08:00).\n\n\nLet me scan through the scheduled tasks and see what's queued up. The workspace backup runs daily, and I notice the quant ops morning inspection should have already kicked in around 09:20 this morning. Let me check if any of these tasks have actually completed or if there's anything waiting to be processed.","thinkingSignature":"f618ff98bbccf392dbfb082b47d93b9690f4157b834c796f7bfc24716a88dfa9"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qwvaxu7b7ucs_1","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qwvaxu7b7ucs_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/active_task_cli.py show --path /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md 2>/dev/null || echo \"NO_ACTIVE_TASK\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":324,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":78360,"totalTokens":78804,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774358418987}}
{"type":"message","id":"5aba2cd0","parentId":"48086f83","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:20:37.044Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_qwvaxu7b7ucs_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Quant Ops\n\n## 08:50 Morning News Push Check\n\n### State File\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查 `status` / `generated_at` / `last_success_at` / `last_failure_at`\n- [ ] 若交易日 08:50 之后仍无当日成功记录，主动汇报阻断原因\n- [ ] 若 `status` 为 `GENERATION_FAILED` 或 `PUSH_FAILED`，主动汇报错误摘要与日志路径\n- [ ] 若已成功且无新增变化，保持安静\n\n## Quant Research Mainline Health\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.json`\n- 终端摘要：`🩺 量化投研主链巡检：OK/WARN/ALERT`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查退出码与 `overall_status`\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报晨报 / 稳定策略 / 回测队列是哪一项断裂\n- [ ] `WARN`：汇报缺口文件或未生成入口\n- [ ] `OK` 且无新增变化：保持安静\n\n## Trading-day Premarket Precheck (09:20-09:40)\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py --available-cash 1000000 --account-nav 930000\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 无需用户提醒，交易日自动执行\n- [ ] 当日已执行过则跳过\n- [ ] 非交易日保持安静\n- [ ] 失败时主动汇报阻断原因与报告路径\n- [ ] 成功时汇报 `precheck` / `orders` / `brief` 路径\n\n## Daily Strategy Audit\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_strategy_audit.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] `PASS`：简要汇报核心指标与路径\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报未通过项与修复建议\n\n## Daily Enhancements\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_enhancements.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_summary.json`\n- `research/reports/daily_enhancement_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 双源验证失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 热力图失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 正常运行：简要汇报上涨/下跌板块数\n\n## Live Dashboard + Feishu Push\n\n### Commands\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_exports.py\npython3 scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_YYYYMMDD.html`\n\n### Push Rules\n- [ ] 成功后主动发飞书 DM：面板路径、precheck 状态、年化/回撤/夏普、买卖记录数、A股温度摘要\n- [ ] `needs_permission=true`：提示给 OpenClaw/终端 Full Disk Access\n- [ ] 导出为空：提示“同花顺暂无可用导出数据/账户为空”\n- [ ] 生成失败：主动发报错摘要与修复建议\n- [ ] 非交易时段不含“可执行买价”，只给预算/优先级/开盘触发条件\n- [ ] 当天已推送且无新增数据，可保持安静\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774358437041}}
