{"type":"message","id":"2dbbf811","parentId":"3324eeae","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:20:59.851Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the state of things:\n\n1. Morning news state - already confirmed OK earlier today\n2. Mainline health - already confirmed OK earlier today\n3. Trading-day premarket precheck (09:20-09:40) - today's trading day, this should have run. Let me check if it ran.\n4. Daily strategy audit - already ran today (PASS confirmed)\n5. Daily enhancements - already ran today (WARN on dual source, OK on heatmap)\n6. Live dashboard + feishu push - already done earlier today\n\nThe premarket precheck (09:20-09:40) - I should check if it ran today. The current time is 21:20, well after the window. Let me check if there's a precheck report for today.\n\n\nSince this is a trading day and 21:20 is well past the 09:20-09:40 window, I need to verify whether the premarket precheck actually executed today. The heartbeat checklist doesn't explicitly track this, but the rules require me to report any failures or blocking issues that occurred during that window.\n\nLooking at what's already been done: morning news, mainline health check, strategy audit, and enhancements all completed successfully, and the dashboard push is finished. So the only outstanding item is confirming the premarket precheck ran. I can see from earlier output that it did generate a report for 20260323, so I should check if there's one for today as well.\n\nSince it's now 21:20 on a trading day, the premarket window has definitely closed. I need to verify whether the precheck ran during that 09:20-09:40 timeframe or if it failed to execute.","thinkingSignature":"03969432d12ab8da13118a01977615fe8983f1e05f4b0864b75f04e15c28aca9"},{"type":"text","text":"今日交易日的盘前窗口（09:20-09:40）已过。先确认盘前 precheck 是否执行过：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_h3bcbh7c1zjo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -t /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/p