{"type":"message","id":"a349399b","parentId":"c2da5d2a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T13:22:47.920Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The precheck status is \"blocked\" but the halt_reason is null/empty. The issue is the `run_live_execution_v1.py` requiring `--trading-mode live`.\n\nThe precheck is blocked because:\n1. The `run_live_execution_v1.py` requires explicit `--trading-mode live` \n2. This was true whether or not the cron ran\n\nNow let me report this to the user. The issues are:\n1. `auto_run_premarket_precheck.py` is NOT in crontab - no automation\n2. When run manually with `--force`, it fails because `run_live_execution_v1.py` needs `--trading-mode live` argument\n\n\n3. Since this is marked as a required heartbeat item, I should escalate this clearly to Zhang Ling rather than trying to fix it silently.","thinkingSignature":"4df93d83a86cd537f0f3afae3515f2d00d49c4fce38bf6e7ac967984e7f9ec6d"},{"type":"text","text":"发现两个问题：**cron 缺失 + 参数缺失**。报告给张玲：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_qjl08wrp0qrl_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"feishu","target":"user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080","message":"🚨 今日盘前 precheck 未执行 — 主动汇报\n\n**状况**：2026-03-24 交易日盘前 precheck 报告缺失（auto_premarket_precheck_20260324.json 不存在），窗口 09:20-09:40 已过。\n\n**阻断原因**：两层问题：\n1. `auto_run_premarket_precheck.py` 未加入 crontab，没有自动化调度\n2. 即使手动用 --force 补跑，底层 `run_live_execution_v1.py` 也报错：`必须显式传入 --trading-mode live`\n\n**当前状态**\n- precheck 报告：blocked（生成但 status=blocked，无 halt_reason）\n- 策略审计：PASS（三盘 runtime_ready=true）\n- 晨报：OK（08:50）\n- 实盘面板：已更新（dashboard_portal + 三盘看板）\n\n**需要的操作**\n需要你确认：\n1. 是否需要为 `auto_run_premarket_precheck.py` 新增 cron 条目（建议 09:20 工作日）？\n2. 是否需要给 `run_live_execution_v1.py` 补 `--trading-mode live` 参数？\n\nprecheck 阻断不影响当日其他链路（策略审计/面板/晨报均正常），但盘前 precheck 缺失意味着当日没有买入方向/预算分配记录，请在开盘前确认是否需要补跑。"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":49143,"output":548,